        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>



        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2853855919" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer14627166076623947618">Superbly researched and written book that brings the stories of hundreds of heroes in to your living room. Difficult to put this book down, and even more difficult to read without weeping. This was truly as Tom Brokaw says, the greatest American generation.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


