      <div id="aboutAuthor" class=" clearFloats bigBox"><div class="h2Container gradientHeaderContainer"><h2 class="brownBackground"><a href="/author/show/5882.Stephen_E_Ambrose">About Stephen E. Ambrose</a></h2></div><div class="bigBoxBody"><div class="bigBoxContent containerWithHeaderContent">
          <div class='bookAuthorProfile'>
<div class='bookAuthorProfile__topContainer'>
<div class='bookAuthorProfile__photoContainer'>
<a href="/author/show/5882.Stephen_E_Ambrose"><div class='bookAuthorProfile__photo' style='background-image: url(https://images.gr-assets.com/authors/1211404212p3/5882.jpg);'></div>
</a></div>
<div class='bookAuthorProfile__widgetContainer'>
<div class='bookAuthorProfile__name'>
<a href="/author/show/5882.Stephen_E_Ambrose">Stephen E. Ambrose
</a></div>
<div class='bookAuthorProfile__followerCount'>
1,769
followers
</div>

</div>
</div>
<div class='bookAuthorProfile__about'>

<span id="freeTextContainer8912319733314320676">Stephen Edward Ambrose was an American historian and biographer of U.S. Presidents Dwight Eisenhower and Richard M. Nixon. He received his Ph.D. in 1960 from the University of Wisconsin-Madison. In his final years he faced charges of plagiarism for his books, with subsequent concerns about his research emerging after his death. <br/><br/></span>

</div>
</div>

<div class="clear"></div></div></div><div class="bigBoxBottom"></div></div>

  

